      <title>Greenko 获得 7.43 亿美元信用额度，用于再融资美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/greenko-gets-743-million-credit-line-to-refinance-dollar-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Greenko 集团已从印度国家基础设施和发展融资银行获得 620 亿卢比（7.43 亿美元）的信用额度，以寻求部分再融资海外债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/greenko-gets-743-million-credit-line-to-refinance-dollar-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 16:23:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
